io.spine.tools.validate.code

Class ConditionalStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.tools.validate.code.ConditionalStatement

  • public final class ConditionalStatement
extends java.lang.Object
    A builder for if - else statements.

    An instance of ConditionalStatement is not reusable. See toCode() doc for the details.
